# Legacy placeholder.
#
# The dispatcher no longer reads this file. UI test accounts are opt-in:
# when a deployment configures the trigger field `ui_accounts_relpath`,
# the test team maintains the pool JSON at
#
#   ${REPO_PATH}/${UI_ACCOUNTS_RELPATH}   (no default; e.g. ifp-data/ifp-common/ifp_users.json)
#
# inside the cloned project repo. The relpath is resolved under the
# project checkout root, NOT under ${REPO_PATH}/${DATA_BASENAME}/.
# When ui_accounts_relpath is unconfigured the dispatcher skips the
# pool flow entirely. See config/README.md and
# scripts/load_ui_accounts.sh for the active contract.
